{"tid":1598810,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"[緊急]大家可唔可以應承我一樣野呀？","createTime":"2019-09-27T16:07:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-27T16:53:54.000Z","uid":137699,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"1edba6a8846cf7055f37f486dace7bfa07b04f7f","tid":1598810,"uid":137699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T16:07:23.000Z","msg":"不知不覺場運動已經經歷左三個半月<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n 一開始既時候都冇估到可以維持咁耐 呢幾個月經歷過好多次高低起伏 身邊唔少人堅持落去 亦有唔少人開始頹左 <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">但我希望係到同大家講聲 <strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong></span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">好希望大家可以繼續一齊行落去 <br />\nSome People Move On. <br />\nBut Not Us ！ </span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n如果你同我一樣見到社會既不公<br />\n如果你同我一樣聽到弱者既控訴<br />\n如果你同我一樣感到正義既怒火<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">咁我懇請各位9.29 同 10.1 上街見</span></span></strong> <br />\n<br />\n無論你出邊到 只有你肯出黎 就一定會帶黎改變！比全世界見識香港人既團結！大家趁仲有時間 做足文宣 叫曬身邊識既人出去 推多d文宣同行動po<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VOWfcUi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVOWfcUi.jpg&h=2db99f4f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TXPAcUj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTXPAcUj.jpg&h=50138f58&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wuPXrek.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwuPXrek.jpg&h=ea082904&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PZgiU7W.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPZgiU7W.jpg&h=7cbd19e0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />